ADDITIONAL NOTICES

Third-party data: The quiz questions and traffic sign images included in this
repository originate from the Italian Patente B exam bank (2023) and were
obtained from Ed0ardo/QuizPatenteB on GitHub, distributed under the MIT
License. This software is not affiliated with or endorsed by the Italian
Ministero delle Infrastrutture e dei Trasporti.

AI-generated content: The English vocabulary definitions stored in the data
files were generated by a local language model and are provided as-is. They
are intended as a study aid and may contain inaccuracies. They should not be
relied upon as authoritative translations for legal or official purposes.

External services: This software may connect to Google Translate (via the
deep-translator library) and dizionario-italiano.it for supplemental
translations and dictionary lookups. Use of these services is subject to
their respective terms of service.
